---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="24/7 Emergency Dentistry in Footscray | Immediate Care for Dental Emergencies"
  description="Facing a dental emergency? Get immediate relief with our emergency dentistry services at Top Dentists Footscray. We handle everything from toothaches to injuries, ensuring prompt and effective care."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Emergency Dentistry</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Emergency Dentistry
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Dental emergencies can happen at any time and often cause significant pain and discomfort. At Top Dentists Footscray, we understand the urgency of these situations and provide prompt emergency dental care to relieve your pain and address your immediate needs.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Whether you're experiencing severe tooth pain, have suffered a dental injury, or are dealing with a broken tooth, our experienced team is ready to help you get back to comfort and health as quickly as possible.
            </p>

            <!-- Emergency Services -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                Our Emergency Response Process
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Rapid assessment</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Quickly assess your situation and take steps to relieve your discomfort.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Comprehensive evaluation</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Perform a thorough examination, take X-rays, and discuss your symptoms to determine the best course of action.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Targeted treatment</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Provide treatment that may involve pain relief, temporary restorations, or other necessary procedures.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Emergency Types -->
            <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Common Dental Emergencies We Treat
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700">Severe Toothaches</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Intense pain requiring immediate attention</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700">Broken or Chipped Teeth</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Trauma or accident-related dental damage</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700">Lost Fillings or Crowns</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Temporary repairs until permanent solutions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700">Dental Abscesses</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Serious infections requiring urgent care</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Comfort and Care -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Your Comfort is Our Priority
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                We understand that dental emergencies can be stressful, and we'll do everything we can to ensure your comfort and well-being throughout the process. Our goal is to get you out of pain and back to your normal routine as quickly as possible.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Action Steps -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  What to Do in a Dental Emergency
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Call us immediately for guidance</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Apply cold compress for swelling</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Save any broken tooth pieces</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Take over-the-counter pain relief as needed</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Emergency Contact
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-red-500">
                  <p class="text-red-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    Call: (03) 9687 5050
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    Available for urgent dental care and guidance during emergencies.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Need Emergency Dental Care?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          For urgent dental care, please call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          immediately or press here to book online
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>